<br>
First off the epic beat the 61 in 5 out of 5 duels.  Both unbuffed.  Worst the epic did was he got down to 1 and a half bubbles of health.  In one battle we DSed the 61 and the epic won with one bubble of life left.<br>
<br>
Secondly, fighting Coldain Bodyguards, the fights lasted on an average 30 to 45 seconds longer with the 61, so I finally got disgusted as it was messing up the timing of the spawns, and switched back to the epic who simply kills them faster.<br>
<br>
I use the 61 when I'm grouped against chain casters and we need stunnage, and when I'm chain peting.  Hard to chain pet with an epic.  Hehe.  I can't imagine ever prefering other than the epic in most situations however.  Mind you I'm only 61 and am not on the Higher Planes yet, where need may require that I alter my thinking due to the epics level.  Hehe...maybe the level limit will prevent the summoning of the lower level Epic in higher planes...hehe.<br>
